  "text": "Such parallels are a far cry from showing some kind of equivalence between the prior-adapted BIC and the model selection tool deriving from M DL, or from bringing P BIC up to the level of the M DL tool. For a more rigorous treatment of the relation between the approaches of M DL and BIC, we refer the reader to [CITATION_1] ]. For present purposes, we restrict attention to some salient differences between the two approaches.",
